  "body": "# üêû Bug Report\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nThe endpoint /eth/v1/node/syncing returns error 500 after upgraded to prysm v2.1.3\r\n\r\n### Has this worked before in a previous version?\r\n\r\nYes it was working fine at v2.1.3-rc.2\r\n\r\n## üî¨ Minimal Reproduction\r\n\r\nBefore upgrade to v2.1.3:\r\n<pre>\r\n  <code>\r\nroot@server:~$ date ; curl -X GET \"http://localhost:3500/eth/v1/node/version\"\r\nMon Jul 11 09:42:26 UTC 2022\r\n{\"data\":{\"version\":\"Prysm/v2.1.3-rc.2 (linux amd64)\"}}\r\nroot@server:~$ date ; curl -X GET \"http://localhost:3500/eth/v1/node/syncing\"\r\nMon Jul 11 09:43:39 UTC 2022\r\n{\"data\":{\"head_slot\":\"106239\",\"sync_distance\":\"3312479\",\"is_syncing\":true}}\r\n  </code>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\nAfter upgrade to v2.1.3:\r\n<pre>\r\n  <code>\r\nroot@server:~$ date ; curl -X GET \"http://localhost:3500/eth/v1/node/version\"\r\nWed Jul 13 08:14:14 UTC 2022\r\n{\"data\":{\"version\":\"Prysm/v2.1.3 (linux amd64)\"}}\r\nroot@server:~$ date ; curl -X GET \"http://localhost:3500/eth/v1/node/syncing\"\r\nWed Jul 13 05:21:24 UTC 2022\r\n{\"message\":\"Could not check optimistic status: could not check if block is optimistic: nil summary returned from the DB\",\"code\":500}\r\n  </code>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n## üî• Error\r\n\r\n<pre><code>\r\nroot@server:~$ date ; curl -X GET \"http://localhost:3500/eth/v1/node/syncing\"\r\nWed Jul 13 05:21:24 UTC 2022\r\n{\"message\":\"Could not check optimistic status: could not check if block is optimistic: nil summary returned from the DB\",\"code\":500}\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n\r\n## üåç  Your Environment\r\n\r\n**Operating System:**\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n  <code>\r\nroot@server:~$ uname -a\r\nLinux server 4.19.0-20-cloud-amd64 #1 SMP Debian 4.19.235-1 (2022-03-17) x86_64 GNU/Linux\r\nroot@server:~$ cat /etc/debian_version \r\n10.12\r\n  </code>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n**What version of Prysm are you running? (Which release)**\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n  <code>\r\nroot@server:~$ date ; curl -X GET \"http://localhost:3500/eth/v1/node/version\"\r\nWed Jul 13 08:14:14 UTC 2022\r\n{\"data\":{\"version\":\"Prysm/v2.1.3 (linux amd64)\"}}\r\nroot@server:~$ ls -l /usr/local/bin/beacon-chain\r\nlrwxrwxrwx 1 root root 56 Jul 13 02:43 /usr/local/bin/beacon-chain -> /opt/prysm-v2.1.3/beacon-chain-v2.1.3-modern-linux-amd64\r\n\r\n  </code>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n**Anything else relevant (validator index / public key)?**\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n  <code>\r\nroot@server:~$ cat /etc/prysm/beacon-chain.yaml\r\ndatadir: /var/lib/prysm/beacon-chain\r\nhttp-web3provider: http://127.0.0.1:8551\r\ngenesis-state: /var/lib/prysm/beacon-chain/genesis.ssz\r\njwt-secret: /etc/eth2/jwtsecret\r\np2p-host-ip: x.x.x.x\r\nslots-per-archive-point: 1\r\n  </code>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n\r\n",
